(724, 2, '2020-12-20 15:26:36', '2020-12-20 15:26:36', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vaadhoo\'s Blue Bowls is a favorite stop for boat charters in the Maldives, not only because it’s a long and smooth righthander, but also because anchoring there means an opportunity to meet the local population and spend time in the local village—one of the great advantages to having amazing waves in a truly unique location.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Surfing in Vaadhoo', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'surfing-in-vaadhoo', '', '', '2020-12-20 17:26:49', '2020-12-20 17:26:49', '', 0, 'http://experiencemaldives.online/?page_id=724', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(725, 2, '2020-12-20 15:26:36', '2020-12-20 15:26:36', '<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>The ¨sea of stars¨ of the Maldives</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Located in the atoll of Raa, we discover Vaadhoo, the island where the ¨sea of stars¨ is found or the sparkling beach of the Maldives.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This&nbsp;<strong>natural phenomenon</strong>, is scientifically known as&nbsp;<strong>bioluminescence</strong>, a process that emerges when plankton has contact with oxygen and unleashes a chemical reaction that is caused from an enzyme named&nbsp;<em>luciferase</em>. This is due to the oxygen that oxidizes a protein named&nbsp;<em>luciferin</em>, when it is in contact with&nbsp;<em>luciferase</em>&nbsp;and moves, it produces a reaction in which the chemical energy becomes a light pollution. The reason in which the blue lights are appreciated on the shore of the beach, in the footsteps of the sand or even the waves plowing by the surfers.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>For this effect to become visible it is necessary that it exists at a constant temperature throughout the day and especially at night.&nbsp;</strong>Therefore, the new moon nights are more ideal to enjoy from this performance in their largest splendour.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Even though this phenomenon can be produced in other places from the Pacific and Atlantic ocean, there are only a few landscapes where the climatology allows this phenomenon to occur in a natural and constant way as in Vaadhoo island of the Maldives. Due to this reason,&nbsp;<strong>the Maldives are considered to be the most impressing place of the world to enjoy the natural light.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Surfing in Vaadhoo', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '724-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-12-20 15:26:36', '2020-12-20 15:26:36', '', 724, 'http://experiencemaldives.online/2020/12/20/724-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
