(809, 2, '2020-12-20 21:12:40', '2020-12-20 21:12:40', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"\" data-et-mouseenter=\"customGoal:BUeeZaTaTaBEKMPXLae:1 customGoal:BUeeHNSPMWdMOdUBMHT:1 customGoal:BUeeHNSPdQEeWFWZTDWFC:1 customGoal:BUeeHNSPMWdMOdUEXXO:1 customGoal:BUeeHNSPdQEeXXaNSPRXXe:1 customGoal:BUeePHOOSINEGO:1 customGoal:BUeeHNSPVadIaCKe:1 customGoal:BUeeHNSPCaASBaRDSGEXO:1 customGoal:BUeeZdbaBMRbBYWKOBLHXT:1\" data-et-click=\"customGoal:BUeeZaTaTaBEKMPXLae:2 customGoal:BUeeHNSPMWdMOdUBMHT:2 customGoal:BUeeHNSPdQEeWFWZTDWFC:2 customGoal:BUeeHNSPMWdMOdUEXXO:2 customGoal:BUeeHNSPdQEeXXaNSPRXXe:2 customGoal:BUeePHOOSINEGO:2 customGoal:BUeeHNSPVadIaCKe:2 customGoal:BUeeHNSPCaASBaRDSGEXO:2 customGoal:BUeeZdbaBMRbBYWKOBLHXT:2\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\">\r\n\r\nMeri Maldives has air-conditioned rooms offering plenty of natural sunlight and free WiFi in Hulhumale. Offering free parking nearby.\r\n\r\nEach tropical-style room features a flat-screen satellite TV, safe, tea/coffee maker and refrigerator. Private bathroom comes with a shower, hairdryer and free toiletries.\r\n\r\nMeri Maldives is 4 km from Malé Airport.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-et-view=\"adUAVYCIFBUYdXfMAPTLKGBfC:1\"></div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples particularly like the location — they rated it <strong>8.7</strong> for a two-person trip.</p>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-we-speak\">We speak your language!</p>', 'Meri Maldives', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'meri-maldives', '', '', '2020-12-20 23:14:31', '2020-12-20 23:14:31', '', 0, 'http://experiencemaldives.online/?post_type=nd_travel_cpt_1&#038;p=809', 0, 'nd_travel_cpt_1', '', 0),
