(849, 2, '2020-12-20 23:28:46', '2020-12-20 23:28:46', 'The Maldive Victory was a cargo ship that sank off the coast of Hulhule on the night of February 13, 1981. Lying upright parallel to the island\'s house reef, she has since become the most famous shipwreck - and one of the hottest dive spots - in the Maldives.\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-853\" src=\"http://experiencemaldives.online/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/187876_3_ca02ef5c7d3cad4bca7144db2a789fc1a7dc4cd9_large-300x193.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"193\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-852\" src=\"http://experiencemaldives.online/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/187874_3_56e970ad04f2d4c371085d48d84ec067c8979810_large-193x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"193\" height=\"300\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-851\" src=\"http://experiencemaldives.online/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/187870_3_2b38417c8536bfc39bffb6a1a88920eb2bd5ba09_large-300x193.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"193\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-850\" src=\"http://experiencemaldives.online/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/187865_3_4a79730d0ac525351affd226a7ff4b9e31a17934_large-1-300x193.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"193\" />', 'MV Victory Shipwreck', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '811-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-12-20 23:28:46', '2020-12-20 23:28:46', '', 811, 'http://experiencemaldives.online/2020/12/20/811-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
